data.description: This duplex home offers 1200 square ft of living space on each side.  Welcoming covered, front porch leads you into this  Spacious house offering a  living room,  large deluxe kitchen and dining room area with laundry room and half bath on the main level.  Upstairs are 3 large bedrooms with a full bath.   Nice location, close to town.  Everyone who qualifies for a FHA or VA loan should consider this house.  Live in one side and rent the other side out.  Win, Win for everyone.
